Author: roseflowr
Text: well i was restricting for a few months before but i reduced it even more the last 3 weeks :(  thank you for the reassurance, i still havent gotten it yet but i took 2 tests and its negative

Author: Somesadie
Text: I think it depends on how much you eat during snacks! It is pretty unlikely to loose your period after 3 weeks, to my knowledge it takes a few months at the earliest. If you are worried about it, try not to fret! Bodies are weird and periods can be late for no reason. It is pretty normal to have it a few days late :)
